<Para RevisionFlag="Changed">To create a new resource record in GDS, use the information from the
<Command>directory show</Command> command to fill in the fields of Mask 21 (<Literal>CDS-Cell</Literal>) 
and Mask 22 (<Literal>CDS-Replica</Literal>) in the GDS administration program.
